/**
 * PageTitle override — intentionally empty.
 *
 * Starlight renders `PageTitle` in its own `ContentPanel`, *above* the markdown
 * body. The prototype article order is `crumbs → h1 → meta-row → lede`
 * (`docs-article.html`), so the H1 must follow the crumbs, not precede them.
 * The H1 is therefore emitted by `ArticleChrome` (rendered just after the
 * crumbs in every article body) instead of here. Rendering it here as well
 * would duplicate the title and place a copy before the crumbs, so this
 * override emits nothing.
 *
 * The docs-home route sets `hero` frontmatter, which makes Starlight skip
 * `PageTitle` entirely (the `DocsHomeHero` override supplies `.home-hero`), so
 * emptying this component has no effect there.
 */
---
